and analytical team
have beamed down, sir.

42:53.112 --> 42:56.531
Ah. What were
the analytical team's findings?

42:56.699 --> 42:58.366
They suggested we reprogram
the system

42:58.534 --> 43:01.494
to correct the readout variables.

43:01.662 --> 43:03.413
Precisely what Commander Data
recommended,

43:03.581 --> 43:05.665
as l recall.

43:08.210 --> 43:10.837
At least it gave Commander Riker
the opportunity

43:11.005 --> 43:13.464
to consider his promotion.

43:13.632 --> 43:16.175
Now that he's accepted,

43:16.343 --> 43:19.512
we can leave him
at Starbase Montgomery.

43:23.517 --> 43:26.477
