With your permission,

43:28.689 --> 43:30.982
l've decided to stay
onboard the Enterprise.

43:37.573 --> 43:38.990
Granted.

43:39.617 --> 43:40.950
Thank you, sir.

43:43.662 --> 43:45.913
Take us out of orbit,
Ensign Crusher.

43:46.081 --> 43:47.874
Breaking synchronous orbit, sir.

43:48.042 --> 43:51.502
Set course for Beta Kupsic.
That is still our destination?

43:51.670 --> 43:54.797
PlCARD: Mm-hm.
- Velocity, warp factor 5.

43:56.216 --> 43:58.509
Course and speed set, sir.

43:59.720 --> 44:03.139
Any particular reason
for this change of heart?

44:03.641 --> 44:05.600
